# Telemetry Requirements for {{ SERVICE_NAME | capitalize }}

Every feature implementation MUST include:

## Required Telemetry
1. **Structured Log**: Emit `event_type: {feature}.{action}` with all required fields
2. **OTEL Span**: Add span for any external API call > 100ms or complex workflow
3. **Metric**: Record `{{ METRIC_PREFIX }}_{feature}_{action}_duration_seconds` histogram + `{{ METRIC_PREFIX }}_{feature}_{action}_total` counter
4. **Correlation IDs**: Include trace_id, span_id{% if multi_tenant %}, tenant_id{% endif %} in all log entries
5. **Event Schema**: Define schema in `telemetry/schemas/{feature}.{ext}`
6. **Alert Rule**: Add if failure rate > 1% or latency p95 > 5s
7. **Dashboard Panel**: Add panel to relevant Grafana dashboard JSON if user-facing

## Log Format
{% if language == "python" %}
```python
logger.info(
    "action_completed",
    event_type="feature.action",
    entity_id=entity_id,
    duration_seconds=duration,
    {% if multi_tenant %}tenant_id=tenant_id,
    {% endif %}trace_id=trace_id,
)
```
{% elif language == "go" %}
```go
logger.Info("action_completed",
    zap.String("event_type", "feature.action"),
    zap.String("entity_id", entityID),
    zap.Float64("duration_seconds", duration),
    {% if multi_tenant %}zap.String("tenant_id", tenantID),
    {% endif %}zap.String("trace_id", traceID),
)
```
{% elif language == "nodejs" %}
```typescript
logger.info("action_completed", {
    event_type: "feature.action",
    entity_id: entityId,
    duration_seconds: duration,
    {% if multi_tenant %}tenant_id: tenantId,
    {% endif %}trace_id: traceId,
});
```
{% elif language == "rust" %}
```rust
tracing::info!(
    event_type = "feature.action",
    entity_id = %entity_id,
    duration_seconds = %duration,
    {% if multi_tenant %}tenant_id = %tenant_id,
    {% endif %}trace_id = %trace_id,
    "action_completed"
);
```
{% endif %}

## Span Format
{% if language == "python" %}
```python
with tracer.start_as_current_span("feature.action") as span:
    span.set_attribute("entity.id", entity_id)
    # ... work ...
```
{% elif language == "go" %}
```go
cctx, span := tracer.Start(ctx, "feature.action")
span.SetAttributes(attribute.String("entity.id", entityID))
defer span.End()
```
{% elif language == "nodejs" %}
```typescript
const span = tracer.startSpan("feature.action");
span.setAttribute("entity.id", entityId);
// ... work ...
span.end();
```
{% elif language == "rust" %}
```rust
let span = info_span!("feature.action", entity.id = %entity_id);
let _guard = span.enter();
// ... work ...
```
{% endif %}

## Metric Format
{% if language == "python" %}
```python
METRICS.record_feature_action(duration=duration_seconds)
METRICS.record_custom_metric(labels={"key": "value"}, value=count)
```
{% elif language == "go" %}
```go
metrics.FeatureActionDuration.Observe(duration)
metrics.CustomMetric.WithLabelValues("value").Add(float64(count))
```
{% elif language == "nodejs" %}
```typescript
metrics.featureActionDuration.observe(duration);
metrics.customMetric.labels("value").inc(count);
```
{% elif language == "rust" %}
```rust
metrics::FEATURE_ACTION_DURATION.observe(duration);
metrics::CUSTOM_METRIC.with_label_values(&["value"]).inc_by(count);
```
{% endif %}

